Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:31.03,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnFZLanTingHei-DB-GBK\fs20\c&H060E1B&\3c&H8AA1A7&\bord2\pos(85.533,255.667)}拥有{\c&H295F81&}翅{\c&H060E1B&}膀与四肢，最强的龙族。\N体力、速度、防御、{\c&H295F81&}智{\c&H060E1B&}力、词术都远超其他种{\c&H295F81&}族{\c&H060E1B&}。
